  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "画面上の漢字のピースを消しながら成語を作るパズルを含む、3つのパズルを楽しむことができます。また、100問の問題に正解することでクリアできる漢字クイズもあります。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "You can enjoy the world of puzzle game magazines published in various ways on GB. Most of the kanji to be asked are 1006 kanji learned in the 1st to 6th grades of elementary school. Acquire perfect while playing antonyms, synonyms, stroke order, okurigana, homophones and idioms. There are four types of games: Kanji quiz \"Spartan Z\", Kanji crossword \"Kankuro\", \"Kanji puzzle\", and original puzzle \"Elephant Dragon\". It can also be used as a kanji learning tool for children from general education.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ],
